# QingHeTian (青禾田) Authorization Description

## Current Authorization Model

### 1. Personal Use - Completely Free
QingHeTian is **completely free** for individual developers, students, open source projects, and non-commercial use.

Authorization method: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)
- Free to use, modify, distribute
- Requires derivative works to also use GPL open source
- See [LICENSE.GPL](LICENSE.GPL) for complete terms

### 2. Commercial Use - Planning Phase
Commercial authorization options are in the planning phase, including:
- Team License (suitable for SMEs)
- Enterprise License (suitable for large organizations)
- Device Authorization (suitable for hardware manufacturers)
- Professional Services (hardware adaptation, custom development, etc.)

Detailed planning: See [COMMERCIAL-LICENSE.md](COMMERCIAL-LICENSE.md)

